description: Welcome to sophisticated urban living to experience & enjoy Boston's vibrant Seaport District at its finest! Step inside this captivating Seaport loft! Custom designed kitchen, designer fixtures & a sun-splashed open floor plan offers modern elegance combined with historic charm in this industrial-flavored 1224 sqft  loft design. The kitchen becomes a focal point for culinary creativity & social interaction, Shaker cabinets offer a timeless design & ample storage, with a peninsula creating seating & counter space, perfect for casual meals or a full-size Dining Area for entertaining guests. The bathroom provides a beautifully tiled walk-in shower, offering a modern & luxurious space to refresh & rejuvenate. Custom sliding barn door accesses your private primary suite with a walk-in closet providing for a streamlined and organized wardrobe. Enjoy spectacular panoramic views of the harbor & city skyline from your roof-deck, easy stroll to Seaport waterfront dining, shopping & recreation.
